I poked a little further, and discovered that when I build 'all' in
VisualStudio, it creates build/lib/i686-pc-win32/cantera_d.lib and then when
I go to do 'make win' from cygwin it is looking for
build/lib/i686-pc-win32/cantera.lib instead.  Is there a discrepency here?
